{"tha-ap216:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap216:0.2":"Hatthivagga ","tha-ap216:0.3":"Ekasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap216:1.1":"“Dumagge pamsukulikam, ","tha-ap216:1.2":"laggam disvana satthuno; ","tha-ap216:1.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap216:1.4":"pamsukulam avandaham. ","tha-ap216:2.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap216:2.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap216:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap216:2.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap216:3.1":"Pancavise ito kappe, ","tha-ap216:3.2":"eko asim janadhipo; ","tha-ap216:3.3":"Amitabhoti namena, ","tha-ap216:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap216:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap216:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap216:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap216:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap216:6.1":"Ekasannakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}